{
  "stem": "24364.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And after the Dutch, the French took over during the Napoleonic Wars, and then the British.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And it-- in our time, it was a British colony.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And now it's independent, has been independent since the mid '60s, I think.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "It's about 800 square miles, the whole island.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "So it's really very, very small, and any number of little cities and towns there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "The capital, as I said, is Port Louis.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And the-- there's lots of jungle there, too, really real jungle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And-- but it's really beautiful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It's now a very, very good holiday place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Lots of people-- I-- I have met so many people now who have gone to Mauritius on holidays.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "You can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "When we were in-- in Europe a couple of years ago, in Vienna there are placards all over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "You want to have a nice holiday, go to Mauritius, honest to god.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And it's-- it's really a very, very beautiful island.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Except the climate is, as I said, not too bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Now apparently, not too good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Now apparently it's mosquito-free.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "In my time, there were lots of mosquitoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And we had lots of malaria.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "That was one of the worst things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "I had malaria 13 times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The inhabitants of Mauritius are mainly Indians who somehow had come over to build something or do something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In my time, there were about 500,000 people living on Mauritius, out of which there were about 200,000 Indians.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The were about 20,000 Chinese, and about 1,500 French still, remnants, really, the-- the richest people in Mauritius.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What-- what was life like in the Mauritius camp?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at the beginning, I remember mainly that it was terribly hot and very unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
